38
00:03:25,125 --> 00:03:26,333
Make it good, Jord.

39
00:03:31,916 --> 00:03:34,666
Please. Make us win, win, win.

40
00:03:34,750 --> 00:03:39,583
-Win! Win! Win!
-Win! Win! Win!

41
00:03:39,666 --> 00:03:41,666
-Win! Win! Win!
-Win! Win! Win!

42
00:03:41,750 --> 00:03:44,500
-Win! Win! Win!
-Win! Win! Win!

43
00:03:44,583 --> 00:03:45,458
Did we do it?

44
00:03:45,541 --> 00:03:47,166
-Sure.
-For real?

45
00:03:47,250 --> 00:03:48,583
Way the hell over there.

46
00:03:49,958 --> 00:03:51,375
Your throw was shit.

47
00:03:52,041 --> 00:03:53,333
