233
00:22:30,916 --> 00:22:35,208
"Fir…"

234
00:22:35,291 --> 00:22:37,541
"Firs… First…"

235
00:22:37,625 --> 00:22:40,375
"First one has ap…"

236
00:22:40,458 --> 00:22:41,666
"First one--"

237
00:22:42,958 --> 00:22:45,333
You're old as fuck and still can't read.

238
00:22:45,416 --> 00:22:46,666
Give it here.

239
00:22:46,750 --> 00:22:47,750
