-Don't do it.

254
00:25:07,125 --> 00:25:08,375
Come out, or else…

255
00:25:08,458 --> 00:25:10,666
Freaking hell, Jord. Jord!

256
00:25:10,750 --> 00:25:11,625
No!

257
00:25:16,708 --> 00:25:18,250
What the hell is that?

258
00:25:19,875 --> 00:25:21,041
Holy shit.

259
00:25:24,875 --> 00:25:26,000
Shit.

260
00:25:30,333 --> 00:25:32,375
Windows. Shut the damn windows.

261
00:25:32,458 --> 00:25:33,583
Shut the windows.

262
00:25:34,666 --> 00:25:35,500
Whoa!

263
00:25:38,125 --> 00:25:39,625
Why are you standing there?

264
00:25:49,250 --> 00:25:50,125
I'm outta here.

265
00:25:51,500 --> 00:25:53,375
-I'm outta here!
-Ton!

266
00:25:54,958 --> 00:25:58,625
